ext10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1000865, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, bless Your vicegerent and the son of Your vicegerents the obedience to whom You have made incumbent upon us and the observance of the right of whom You have made obligatory and from whom You have removed filth and whom You have purified with thorough purifying. O Allah, give him victory and make him the supporter of Your religion and through him, give victory to Your and his adherents, followers, and backers. Include us with them.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Apne wali aur apne auliya ke (nasl dar nasl) farzand par rehmat naazil farma jin ki ita’at Tu ne laazim farmayi, unka haq waajib kiya aur un se har najaasat ko dur rakkha aur unhe woh paak o paakeeza rakkha jo unka haq hai. Ay Mabood! Imam’e Zamaana (a.t.f.s) ki madad farma aur unke zariye apne deen ko ghalaba de, aur unke zariye apne dosto’n, unke dosto’n, unke shiyo’n aur madad gaaro’n ko quwwat de aur hamein un mein se qaraar de.", "Urdu": "اے معبود!اپنے ولی اور اپنے اولیاء کے(نسل در نسل) فرزند پر رحمت نازل فرما جن کی اطاعت تو نے لازم فرمائی ان کا حق واجب کیا اور ان سے ناپاکی کو دور کیا انہیں پاک رکھا اور خوب پاک۔ اے معبود! امام زمانؑہ کی مدد کران کے ذریعے اپنے دین کو غلبہ دے اور ان کے ذریعے اپنے دوستوں، ان کے دوستوں شیعوں اور مدد گاروں کو قوت دے اور ہمیں ان میں سے قرار دے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA WALIYYEKA WABNE AWLEYAAA-EKAL LAZEENA FARAZTA TAA-A’TAHUM WA AWJABTA HAQQAHUM WA AZHABTA A’NHOMUR RIZSA WA TAHHARTAHUM TATHEERAN ALLAAHUMMAN SURHO WANTASIR BEHI LEDEENEKA WANSUR BEHI AWLEYAAA-AKA WA ALWEYAA-AHU WA SHEE-A’TAHU WA ANSAARAHU WAJ-A’LNAA MINHUM.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی وَلِیِّكَ وَابْنِ اَوْلِیَآئِكَ الَّذِیْنَ فَرَضْتَ طَاعَتَهُمْ وَاَوْجَبْتَ حَقَّهُمْ وَاَذْهَبْتَ عَنْهُمُ الرِّجْسَ وَطَهَّرْتَهُمْ تَطْهِیْرًا۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ انْصُرْهُ وَانْتَصِرْ بِهٖ لِدِیْنِكَ وَانْصُرْ بِهٖ اَوْلِیَآئَكَ وَاَوْلِیَآئَهٗ وَشِیْعَتَهٗ وَاَنْصَارَهٗ وَاجْعَلْنَا مِنْهُمْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1000868, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah protect him against the evil of every transgressor and tyrant and against the evils of all Your creatures. Guard him from ahead of him, behind him, his right side, and his left side. Watch him and defend him against anything that may cause evil to him. Save through him Your Messenger and the family of Your Messenger. Manifest justice through him. Aid him with victory. Help his backers.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Bachaaye rakh unko har baaghi aur sarkash ke sharr (evil) se aur apni makhluqaat ke sharr se unko mehfooz rakh. Unke aaghe (front) se aur unke peechhe (back) se, unke daaye (right) se aur unke baaye (left) se unki nigheh-baani farma, unko (dushmano ke sharr se) bachaaye rakh, keh woh unhe koi aziyat pohonchaye unki hifaazat farma. Apne Rasool (s.a.w.a) aur unke Aale paak (a.s) ki hifaazat farma aur Imam’e aakhir ke zariye adl o insaaf ko zaahir kar aur unhe nusrat (madad) de kar unko qavi (taaqat-war) bana. aur unke naasir (nusrat karne waalo’n) ki madad farma.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! ان کو ہرباغی اور سرکش کے شر سے بچائے رکھ اور اپنی مخلوقات کے شر سے ان کو محفوظ رکھ ان کے آگے سے ان کے پیچھے سے ان کے دائیں سے اور ان کے بائیں سے ان کی نگہبانی کر ان کو بچائے رکھ اس سے کہ انہیں کوئی اذیت پہنچے ان کی حفاظت کر کے اپنے رسولؐ اور ان کی آل ؑ کی حفاطت کر ان امام آخرؑکے ذریعے عدل کوظاہر کر اور نصرت دے کر ان کو قوی بنا ان کے ناصروں کی مدد فرما۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA A-I’ZHO MIN SHARRE KULLE BAAGHIN WA TAAGHIN WA MIN SHARRE JAMEE-E’ KHALQEKA WAH-FAZHO MIM BAYNE YADAYHE WA MIN KHALFEHI WA A’YN YAMEENEHI WA A’N SHEMAALEHI WAHRUSHO WAM-NA’HO MIN AYN YOOSALA ELAYHE BE SOOO-IN WAHFAZHO FEEHE RASOOLAKA WA AALA RASOOLEKA WA AZHIR BEHIL A’DLA WA AYYIDHO BIN-NASRE WANSUR NAASEREEHE.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اَعِذْهُ مِنْ شَرِّ كُلِّ بَاغٍ وَّطَاغٍ وَّمِنْ شَرِّ جَمِیْعِ خَلْقِكَ وَاحْفَظْهُ مِنْۢ بَیْنِ یَدَیْهِ وَمِنْ خَلْفِهٖ وَعَنْ یَّمِیْنِهٖ وَعَنْ شِمَالِهٖ وَاحْرُسْهُ وَامْنَعْهُ مِنْ اَنْ یُّوْصَلَ اِلَیْهِ بِسُوْٓءٍ وَّاحْفَظْ فِیْهِ رَسُوْلَكَ وَاٰلَ رَسُوْلِكَ وَاَظْهِرْ بِهِ الْعَدْلَ وَاَیِّدْهُ بِالنَّصْرِ وَانْصُرْ نَاصِرِیْهِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1000870, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Frustrate those who intend to disappoint him. Terminate those who intend to eradicate him. And, through him, terminate the tyrants of unbelief, kill the disbelievers, the hypocrites, and all atheists, wherever they are; in the east or the west of the earth on the lands or in the oceans, and, through him, fill in the earth with justice, manifest the religion of Your Prophet, blessings and peace of You be upon him and his Household, make me.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Unko Tu chhod de jo un (Imam’e Zamaana a.t.f.s) ko chhod gaye, aur unko (Imam a.s. ko) kamzor karne waalo’n ki kamar tod de. Unke haatho’n kufr ke sardaaro’n ko zer kar (shikast de) aur unki talwaar se kaafiro’n, munafiqo’n aur saare be-deeno ko qatl kara de, woh jahan jahan hai chahe zameen ke mashriqo’n (east) aur uske maghribo’n (west) mein maidaano aur samandaro’n mein (kahi bhi ho) unke (Imam a.s ke) zariye zameen ko adl se bhar de aur apne Nabi (s.a.w.a) ke deen ko ghaalib (kaamyaab) kar de.", "Urdu": "ان کو چھوڑ دے جو ان کو چھوڑ گئے ان کو کمزور کرنے والوں کی کمر توڑ دے ان کے ہاتھوں کفر کے سرداروں کو زیر کر ان کی تلوار سے کافروں،منافقوں اور سارے بے دینوں کو قتل کرا دے وہ جہاں جہاں ہیں زمین کے مشرقوں اور اس کے مغربوں میں میدانوں اور سمندروں میں ان کے ذریعے زمین کو عدل سے بھر دے اور اپنے نبی ؐ کے دین کو غالب کر دے۔", "RArabic": "WAKHZUL KHAAZELEEHE WAQSIM QAASEMEEHE WAQSIM BEHI JABAABERATAL KUFRE WAQTUL BEHIL KUFFAARA WAL MONAAFEQEENA WA JAMEE-I’L MULHEDEENA HAYSO KAANU MIM MASHAAREQIL ARZE WA MAGHAAREBEHAA BARREHAA WA BAHREHAA WAM-LAA BEHIL ARZA A’DLAN WA AZHIR BEHI DEENA NABIYYEKA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAIHE WA AALEHI WA SALLAM WAJ-A’LNEE.", "ArabicText1": "وَاخْذُلْ خَاذِلِیْهِ وَاقْصِمْ قَاصِمِیْهِ وَاقْصِمْ بِهٖ جَبَابِرَۃَ الْكُفْرِ وَاقْتُلْ بِهِ الْكُفَّارَ وَالْمُنَافِقِیْنَ وَجَمِیْعَ الْمُلْحِدِیْنَ حَیْثُ كَانُوْا مِنْ مَّشَارِقِ الْاَرْضِ وَمَغَارِبِهَا بَرِّهَا وَبَحْرِهَا وَامْلَا بِهِ الْاَرْضَ عَدْلًا وَّاَظْهِرْ بِهٖ دِیْنَ نَبِیِّكَ صَلَّی اللہُ عَلَیْهِ وَاٰلِهٖ وَسَلَّمْ وَاجْعَلْنِیْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016767, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, of his supporters, helpers, followers, and adherents; allow me to see the hopes of the family of Muhammad, peace be upon them, come true, and the hazards of their enemies come true. O God of Truth, respond.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aur ay Ma’bood! Mujhe Imam Mahdi (a.t.f.s) ke madad gaaro’n, unke saathiyo’n, unke pairo kaaro’n (followers) aur unke shiyo’n mein se qaraar de, aur Aale Muhammad (a.s) ke baare mein jis ki woh tamanna rakhte hai aur unke dushmano mein jis se woh dur rehte hai mere liye aashkaar (waazeh) farma, ay sachche Ma’bood aisa hi ho.", "Urdu": "اور اے معبود! مجھے امام مہدیؑ کے مدد گاروں، ان کے ساتھیوں، ان کے پیروکاروں اور ان کے شیعوں میں سے قرار دے اورآل محمؑد کے بارے میں جس کی وہ تمنا رکھتے ہیں اور ان کے دشمنوں میں جس سے وہ دور رہتے ہیں میرے لئے آشکار فرما اے سچے معبود! ایسا ہی ہو۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA MIN ANSAAREHI WA A-A'WAANEHI WA ATBAA-E'HI WA SHEE-A'TEHI WA ARENEE FEE AALE MOHAMMADIN A’LAIHEMUS SALAAMO MAA YAMALOONA WA FEE A'DUWWEHIM MAA YAHZAROONA ELAAHAL HAQQE AAMEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ مِنْ اَنْصَارِهٖ وَاَعْوَانِهٖ وَاَتْبَاعِهٖ وَشِیْعَتِهٖ وَاَرِنِیْ فِیْٓ اٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ عَلَیْهِمُ السَّلَامُ مَا یَاْمَلُوْنَ وَفِیْ عَدُوِّهِمْ مَا یَحْذَرُوْنَ اِلٰهَ الْحَقِّ اٰمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": n